metadata.name: Unrevealed-RugRatz
metadata.description: By TEAM RUGGIEZ  The ’90s are back with RugRatz NFT, the first collection from Team Ruggiez! 2500 collectible NFT’s driven by the community. Every RugRatz NFT will give holders access to a host of benefits such as governance voting rights, exclusive access to our holder Discord channel, automatic whitelisting, minting discounts, IRL event access for upcoming parties, and the possibility of passive income from our casino (NFT’s with gold, silver or bronze diapers & gold crowns ONLY).
